column3:
Since `map.erase(it)` invalidates `it` I was doing a double-pass to avoid incrementing `it`. However, it turns out `erase` will [return the Iterator](https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/container/map/erase) following the last removed element. So I've updated the code to use that.

